  <Gun_TurretSniper.label>鈾彈砲塔</Gun_TurretSniper.label>
  <!-- EN: A self-loading uranium slug cannon designed to attach to a turret. -->
  <Gun_TurretSniper.description>一種安裝到砲塔上，可自動裝填鈾彈的砲塔。</Gun_TurretSniper.description>
